{"tid":54617,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"私訊考生陪睡能當空姐 中國海南航空面試官遭開除","createTime":"2016-12-25T16:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T03:34:30.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9373e58dfd7cb7ee85b83b7f147d805edaf590f6","tid":54617,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T16:39:05.000Z","msg":"2016-12-22 23:12 <br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國海南航空爆出，一名面試主考官私訊女考生，以身體換取空姐一職的醜聞。海南航空在查實該事件後，已將該名面試官開除。 <br />\n<br />\n據《澎湃新聞》，中國海南航空一名面試官，私訊一名面試女考生，首先問她離開考場沒，隨即調戲對方祭出「我能夠帶你進海航，但你需要付出一些東西」的試探性問話，該名女考生回覆：「錢嗎？」，未料卻遭對方回應：「如果是人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？」，但遭到該女考生拒絕。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpAIM6dr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpAIM6dr.jpg&h=e50eafd0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n兩方對話被舉報後，該名面試官隨即遭海南航空開除。（圖擷自微博） <br />\n<br />\n面試官用潛規則性騷擾考生事件傳開，海南航空在經查實該項舉報後，在微博上發表致歉聲明，指出已將涉事人員開除，並保留後續向其追究法律責任的權利，也將繼續加強員工個人道德教育，歡迎各界的共同監督。 <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1925719\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1925719&d=gTyQCL0llkviVWn5Pni7IqEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=9f14464c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1925719&h=806a4161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1925719</a>"},{"pid":"c302d787f8820f889652708305afec7e0ab8b073","tid":54617,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T16:40:57.000Z","msg":"空姐係都有技術需求係指呢樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c9e06f4b3a5ae6de3d9e39e79a78a945dd80f5","tid":54617,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T16:41:52.000Z","msg":"扮晒道德<br />\n<br />\n不嬲D女成日同高層上床架啦"},{"pid":